          <span style="width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%; background:#D6EEE0; border:3px solid #FBFCFE; margin-left:-12px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:#15724A;">M</span>
          <span style="width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%; background:#F7E4C4; border:3px solid #FBFCFE; margin-left:-12px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:#8A4B00;">J</span>
        </div>
        <span style="font-size:15px; font-weight:500; color:#536084; max-width:230px; line-height:1.4;">Built with neurologists, movement-disorder nurses, and the people who use it.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PHONE MOCKUP -->
