          <span style="width:40px; height:40px; flex:none; border-radius:12px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.18); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none"><rect x="3.5" y="9" width="21" height="10" rx="5" transform="rotate(-45 14 14)" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.4"></rect><path d="M11 11 17 17" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></span>
          <div style="flex:1;"><div style="font-size:17px; font-weight:800; color:#fff;">Take dose at 11:45</div><div style="font-size:13px; font-weight:500; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">Levodopa / Carbidopa 25/100</div></div>
