          <p style="font-size:15.5px; line-height:1.6; font-weight:500; color:#536084; margin:0 0 18px;">the foundation. every second of ankle motion is scored against the physiological signature of a freeze, the walking rhythm collapsing into a trembling one. it's what fills the freeze log and grounds everything above it.</p>
          <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; border-top:1px solid #ECF0F7; padding-top:16px;">
