            <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px;"><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:600; color:#8A96B0;">measured on</span><span style="font-size:14px; font-weight:800; color:#16203A;">real freeze recordings, 2 cohorts</span></div>
