        <div style="font-size:15px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:1.6px; color:{{ accent }}; margin-bottom:14px;">WHAT IT TAKES TO WORK</div>
        <h2 style="font-size:clamp(28px,5.2vw,42px); line-height:1.12; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-1.1px; margin:0 0 18px;">From the box to a forecast that's yours.</h2>
        <p style="font-size:19px; line-height:1.6; font-weight:500; color:#3A4A66; max-width:640px; margin:0 auto;">Cadence isn't accurate out of the box for everyone, it becomes accurate for you. Here's the setup that makes that happen, and who's involved at each step.</p>
