            <div style="display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;"><h3 style="font-size:20px; font-weight:800; margin:0 0 8px;">bounds set by your doctor, before any nudge</h3><span style="font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:#8A96B0;">YOUR CLINICIAN</span></div>
            <p style="font-size:16px; line-height:1.6; font-weight:500; color:#536084; margin:0;">every dose nudge lives inside limits your neurologist sets, earliest, latest, maximum per day. cadence times within the plan; it never writes the plan. anything the model wants to do outside those bounds is suppressed, not softened.</p>
