            <div style="display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:12px; flex-wrap:wrap;"><h3 style="font-size:20px; font-weight:800; margin:0 0 8px;">it keeps learning, carefully</h3><span style="font-size:13px; font-weight:700; color:#8A96B0;">AUTOMATIC, GATED</span></div>
