          <div style="padding:20px 18px; background:#16203A; font-size:15px; font-weight:800; color:#7CF0B7;">cadence<div style="font-size:12.5px; font-weight:600; color:#8597B5; margin-top:3px;">two bands, one forecast</div></div>
